high_descs: Walk up to the bed in front of you.
Pick up the book on the bed to the left of the cushion.
Turn and walk to the black desk on the right.
Put the book down on the desk in front of the lamp.
Turn and walk back to the bed.
Pick up the remaining book from the bed.
Turn and walk back to the desk on the right.
Place the book to the right of the pen on the desk.
anns.task_desc: To move two books and place them on the desk.

high_descs: Turn right and take one step, turn left for two steps then stop to face the bed.
Pick up the Clean Code handbook that is farthest right and closest to you.
Turn around and take seven steps, turn right and walk to the desk and stop.
Place the handbook on the desk front, just to the left of the pen in front of the chair.
Turn around and take one step, turn left, walk to the bed and stop.
Pick up the remaining Clean Code handbook from the bed.
Turn around and take seven steps, turn right and walk to the desk and stop.
Place the handbook on the desk front, just to the right of the pen in front of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place two Clean Code handbooks on the desk

high_descs: Head straight to the bed
Grab the book off of the bed
Turn around and go to the desk
Put the book on the desk
Turn right and go to the bed
Grab the book off of the bed
Turn around and go to the desk
Put the book on the desk to the right of the other book
anns.task_desc: Put two books on top of the desk
